{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/siapa-pencetus-mata-besar-berkilauan-di-anime-dan-manga-jepang/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Siapa Pencetus Mata Besar Berkilauan di Anime dan Manga Jepang?","content":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Pernah gak sih kalian bertanya-tanya siapa awal pencetus dan yang pertama kali mempopulerkan mata besar berkilauan khas di manga dan anime? Apa itu asli original dari kreator Jepang? Atau terinspirasi dari suatu hal? Nah, dari dulu-dulu kita baca manga, bentuk mata yang besar dan berkilauan memang sudah identik banget.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_21855\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-21855\" data-attachment-id=\"21855\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/jangan-ngaku-punya-nyali-kalau-gak-berani-nonton-film-horror-klasik-di-bawah-ini/attachment/isi-15/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/isi-15.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Mata besar berkilauan khas anime dan manga.  Sumber: Google Images\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Mata besar berkilauan khas anime dan manga.  Sumber: Google Images&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/isi-15.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/isi-15.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-21855\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/isi-15.jpg\" alt=\"Mata besar berkilauan khas anime dan manga. Sumber: Google Images\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-21855\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Mata besar berkilauan khas anime dan manga. Sumber: Google Images</p></div></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kalau ngomongin soal anime atau manga, pasti nama yang terbesit di kepala adalah Hayao Miyazaki, Fujiko F. Fujio, Masashi Kishimoto, Akira Toriyama, Eiichiro Oda, Gosho Aoyama dan lain-lain. Namun memangnya bro sis gak penasaran sama pelopor manga dan anime di Jepang?</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Komik Jepang sukses menginvasi Indonesia sejak era Kungfu Boy, Dragon Ball kemudian dilanjutkan dengan Naruto, One Piece dan komik romance lainnya. Seperti yang diketahui ciri, khas dari manga dan anime adalah bola mata karakternya yang besar dan berkilauan.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_21858\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-21858\" data-attachment-id=\"21858\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/jangan-ngaku-punya-nyali-kalau-gak-berani-nonton-film-horror-klasik-di-bawah-ini/attachment/isi-16/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/isi-16.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Osamu Tezuka. Sumber: Japan Info\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Osamu Tezuka. Sumber: Japan Info&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/isi-16.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/isi-16.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-21858\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/isi-16.jpg\" alt=\"Osamu Tezuka. Sumber: Japan Info\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-21858\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Osamu Tezuka. Sumber: Japan Info</p></div></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nah, style komik Jepang dengan bola mata besar berkilauan merupakan ciptaan dari mangaka yang bernama Osamu Tezuka. Inspirasi bola mata besar ini ia dapatkan dari kartun Disney Bambi dan Betty Boop.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_21867\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-21867\" data-attachment-id=\"21867\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/jangan-ngaku-punya-nyali-kalau-gak-berani-nonton-film-horror-klasik-di-bawah-ini/attachment/isi-19/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/isi-19.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Betty Boop. Sumber: Quora\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Betty Boop. Sumber: Quora&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/isi-19.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/isi-19.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-21867\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/isi-19.jpg\" alt=\"Betty Boop. Sumber: Quora\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-21867\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Betty Boop. Sumber: Quora</p></div></p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_21873\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-21873\" data-attachment-id=\"21873\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/jangan-ngaku-punya-nyali-kalau-gak-berani-nonton-film-horror-klasik-di-bawah-ini/attachment/isi-21/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/isi-21.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Bambi. Sumber: Quora\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Bambi. Sumber: Quora&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/isi-21.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/isi-21.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-21873\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/isi-21.jpg\" alt=\"Bambi. Sumber: Quora\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-21873\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Bambi. Sumber: Quora</p></div></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Osamu Tezuka juga dikenal sebagai God of Manga dan Godfather of Anime. Pada tahun 1946, Osamu sensei mempublikasikan manga pertama dalam sejarah Jepang yang berjudul Diary of Ma-Chan. Diary of Ma- Chan terdiri dari beberapa panel dan dipublikasikan oleh surat kabar Jepang. Kemudian dilanjutkan pada tahun 1963, anime karya Ozamu yang berjudul Testuwan Astro atau Astro Boy pun diproduksi anime-nya.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_21879\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-21879\" data-attachment-id=\"21879\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/jangan-ngaku-punya-nyali-kalau-gak-berani-nonton-film-horror-klasik-di-bawah-ini/attachment/isi-23/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/isi-23.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Manga pertama di Jepang, Diary of Ma-Chan. Sumber: TezukaOsamu.net\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Manga pertama di Jepang, Diary of Ma-Chan. Sumber: TezukaOsamu.net&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/isi-23.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/isi-23.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-21879\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/isi-23.jpg\" alt=\"Manga pertama di Jepang, Diary of Ma-Chan. Sumber: TezukaOsamu.net\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-21879\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Manga pertama di Jepang, Diary of Ma-Chan. Sumber: TezukaOsamu.net</p></div></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sebenarnya Astro Boy bukanlah anime pertama Jepang. Jauh pada tahun 1917, terdapat animasi berdurasi 2 menit yang menampilkan seorang samurai sedang mangayunkan pedangnya. Animasi yang berjudul Namakura Gatana ini dibuat oleh Oten Shimokawa dan Seitarou Kitayama. Meski begitu, Astro Boy merupakan anime pertama yang sukses di dunia internasional.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_21870\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-21870\" data-attachment-id=\"21870\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/jangan-ngaku-punya-nyali-kalau-gak-berani-nonton-film-horror-klasik-di-bawah-ini/attachment/isi-20/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/isi-20.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Kalau diperhatikan, mata Astro Boy memang sekilas mirip dengan mata Bambi dan Betty Boop ya? Sumber: quora\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Kalau diperhatikan, mata Astro Boy memang sekilas mirip dengan mata Bambi dan Betty Boop ya? Sumber: quora&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/isi-20.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/isi-20.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-21870\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/isi-20.jpg\" alt=\"Kalau diperhatikan, mata Astro Boy memang sekilas mirip dengan mata Bambi dan Betty Boop ya? Sumber: quora\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-21870\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Kalau diperhatikan, mata Astro Boy memang sekilas mirip dengan mata Bambi dan Betty Boop ya? Sumber: quora</p></div></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Dr. Osamu Tezuka lahir pada tahun 3 November 1928 di Prefektur Osaka. Beliau dianggap sebagai seorang pionir dalam teknik dan genre-genre manga. Mengawali karir sebagai dokter, Tezuka kemudian beralih menggambar manga. Semasa hidupnya, Tezuka telah menghasilkan lebih dari 700 manga loh bro sis!</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_21882\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-21882\" data-attachment-id=\"21882\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/jangan-ngaku-punya-nyali-kalau-gak-berani-nonton-film-horror-klasik-di-bawah-ini/attachment/isi-24/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/isi-24.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Osamu Tezuka dan tumpukan komik Astro Boy-nya. Sumber: tofugu.com\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Osamu Tezuka dan tumpukan komik Astro Boy-nya. Sumber: tofugu.com&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/isi-24.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/isi-24.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-21882\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/isi-24.jpg\" alt=\"Osamu Tezuka dan tumpukan komik Astro Boy-nya. Sumber: tofugu.com\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-21882\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Osamu Tezuka dan tumpukan komik Astro Boy-nya. Sumber: tofugu.com</p></div></p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"add9524a-f35e-5de3-9cb6-9b32b386caea"}}}